        <article id="post-文档-Markdown使用小技巧" class="article article-type-post" itemscope itemprop="blogPost">
    
        <h1 class="article-title">Markdown使用小技巧</h1>
    
    <div class="article-meta">
        
        
        
        <span class="book">
            <i class="iconfont icon-category"></i>
            
            
            <a  data-rel="小技巧">小技巧</a> > 
            
            <a  data-rel="小技巧&lt;---&gt;文档">文档</a>
            
        </span>
        
        
        <span class="tag">
            <i class="iconfont icon-tag"></i>
            
            <a class="color4">markdown</a>
            
        </span>
        
    </div>
    <div class="article-meta">
        
            发布时间 : <time class="date" title='最后更新: 2021-05-28 14:37:58'>2021-05-24 11:14</time>
        
    </div>
    <div class="article-meta">
        
        <span>字数:140</span>
        
        
        
    </div>
    
    <div class="toc-ref">
    
        <ol class="toc"><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#1-%E6%89%93%E5%AF%B9%E5%8B%BE-%E5%AF%B9%E5%8F%B7"><span class="toc-text">1. 打对勾&#x2F;对号</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#2-%E7%A9%BA%E6%A0%BC%E7%9A%84%E5%8C%BA%E5%88%AB"><span class="toc-text">2. 空格的区别</span></a></li></ol>
    
